# Roll20 Macro Examples for AI Dungeon Master

These macros speed up common commands. Copy-paste into Roll20 Macro bar.

## Player Macros

### Quick Action
**Name:** AI Action
**Macro:**
```
!aidm ?{What do you do?}
```

### Request Turn
**Name:** My Turn
**Macro:**
```
!aidm myturn
```

### Quick Skill Check (with token selection)
**Name:** Skill Check
**Macro:**
```
!aidm roll ?{Skill|perception|stealth|athletics|investigation}
```

### Persona Quick-Switch (GM only)
**Name:** Change Mood
**Macro:**
```
!aidm persona ?{DM Persona|classic|gothic|whimsical|cosmic|noir|tavern}
```

### Common Actions (create separate macros or use dropdown)
**Name:** Quick Actions
**Macro:**
```
!aidm ?{Choose Action|I search the room|I listen carefully|I ready my weapon|I examine it closely|I try to hide}
```

## GM Macros

### Process Queue
**Name:** [GM] Dump Queue
**Macro:**
```
!aidm_dump
```
*Copy the whispered JSON to relay page*

### Clear Queue (Emergency)
**Name:** [GM] Clear Queue
**Macro:**
```
!aidm_clear
```

### Advance Turn
**Name:** [GM] Next Turn
**Macro:**
```
!aidm next
```

### Help Reference
**Name:** AI DM Help
**Macro:**
```
!aidm help
```

## Advanced Macros

### Combat Action with Roll
**Name:** Attack
**Macro:**
```
!aidm I attack with my ?{Weapon|sword|bow|staff|dagger}
!aidm roll attack
```
*Note: Executes two commands. May need to be split.*

### Contextual Investigation
**Name:** Investigate
**Macro:**
```
!aidm I carefully examine the ?{Target|door|chest|body|altar|bookshelf}
!aidm roll investigation
```

### Quick Persona Samples (for testing)
**Name:** [GM] Test Personas
**Macro:**
```
!aidm persona classic
!aidm The heroes gather in the tavern
```
*Change persona and send test narration*

## Tips

- **Bar 1:** Player actions (Quick Action, My Turn, Skill Check)
- **Bar 2:** GM controls (Dump Queue, Next Turn, Persona)
- **Token Macros:** Attach skill checks to character sheets
- **Visibility:** Make player macros visible to all, GM macros visible to GM only

## Custom Prompt Templates

For more immersive actions, create macros with narrative templates:

### Stealth Approach
```
!aidm I move silently toward the ?{Target}, staying in the shadows and watching for ?{Threat|guards|traps|movement}
```

### Social Interaction
```
!aidm I approach ?{NPC} and try to ?{Action|persuade|intimidate|deceive|charm} them about ?{Topic}
```

### Spellcasting
```
!aidm I cast ?{Spell} targeting ?{Target}, focusing my energy on ?{Intent}
```

